{"word":"συνθάπτω","slug":"συνθάπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνθάπτω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) </el><p/><i>to bury together, join in burying</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τινά τινι</el> one <i>with</i> another, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be buried with</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/>"}]}